title: Bug 104630: Column icons don't show up in connecting Derby database
OB: When expanding the Data Source in the Available Items sector by clicking the related icon, the column icons do not appear.
EB: When expanding the Data Source in the Available Items sector by clicking the related icon, the column icons should be displayed.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the software and navigate to the Available Items sector. 
2. Locate the Data Source and click on its corresponding icon to expand it. 
3. Observe that the column icons are not displayed.
